Create a class called Order

The class should have these attributes :
    customer_name 
    items 

Create a method called add_item(name, price)
    Adds item to the items dictionary
    Price must be greater than 0
    If item already exists → do not add again

Create an instance method called get_total():
    Calculates and returns the total price of all items

Create get_order_type() instance method: 
    If total ≥ 100 → print "Expensive Order"
    Else → print "Normal Order"
